<paragraph blockId="2.[144,1104,1293,1701]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270">
It has been reported that some species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Melin" authorityYear="1939" box="[645,759,1293,1317]" class="Malacostraca" family="Paguridae" genus="Pagurixus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[645,759,1293,1317]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270">Pagurixus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
have a collar-like protrusion located on the posteromesial portion of the right coxa of the fifth pereopod in males (Komai and 
<bibRefCitation author="Myorin E" box="[300,456,1357,1381]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" pagination="1 - 12" refId="ref33305" refString="Komai T and Myorin E. 2005. A new species of Pagurixus (Crustacea: Decapoda: Anomura: Paguridae) from southern Japan. Zootaxa 876: 1 - 12." type="journal article" year="2005">Myorin 2005</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Komai T" box="[474,770,1357,1381]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" pagination="507 - 516" refId="ref33173" refString="Komai T. 2006. A new species of Pagurixus Melin, 1939 (Crustacea: Decapoda: Anomura: Paguridae) from the Ryukyu Islands, Japan. Zoosystema 28: 507 - 516." type="journal article" year="2006">Komai and Osawa 2006</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Komai T" box="[794,1103,1357,1381]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" pagination="507 - 516" refId="ref33173" refString="Komai T. 2006. A new species of Pagurixus Melin, 1939 (Crustacea: Decapoda: Anomura: Paguridae) from the Ryukyu Islands, Japan. Zoosystema 28: 507 - 516." type="journal article" year="2006">Komai and Osawa (2006)</bibRefCitation>
termed this structure “posteromesial protrusion”. The presence of this protrusion is now confirmed in the following nine species (although the developmental degree of it is rather variable according to species): 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Melin" baseAuthorityYear="1939" box="[615,763,1453,1477]" class="Malacostraca" family="Paguridae" genus="Pagurixus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="boninensis">
